Sub-policy 1
https://help.auraframes.com/hc/articles/218345938:
We use essential cookies for site performance to deliver the best possible shopping experience for you, our customers. With your consent, we may also use nonessential cookies to improve your experience. By clicking “Accept” you agree to our
Privacy Policy
. You can manage these settings at any time by clicking Preferences.
Preferences
Essential
These essential cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be disabled. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.
Functional
These nonessential cookies are used to enhance the functionality of the site. They do not store directly personal information, but do uniquely identify your browser and internet device. By disabling, certain features and experiences on the site may not work.
Performance
These nonessential cookies are used to enhance the performance of the site. All information these cookies collect is aggregated and therefore anonymous. By disabling, we will not know that you have visited the site.
Marketing
These nonessential cookies are used to make advertisements more relevant to you. A profile is created regarding your browsing interests and behavior, and is used to customize the ads you see. By disabling, you will experience less targeted advertising.
About
Cookies are small text files that can be used by websites to make a user's experience more efficient.
The law states that we can store cookies on your device if they are strictly necessary for the operation of this site. For all other types of cookies we need your permission.
This site uses different types of cookies. Some cookies are placed by third party services that appear on our pages.
You can at any time change or withdraw your consent from the Cookie Declaration on our website.
